    "subject": "Bihar Geography",
    "topic": "Geographical Scenario",
    "question": "Consider the following statements regarding the various geographical aspects of Bihar -\nI. Agriculture contributes nearly 67 per cent to Bihar's domestic product.\nII. Silk industry in Bihar provides self-employment to over 1,50,000 people\nIII. About 47 lakh acres of land in Bihar get flooded every year, while 10 lakh acres remain permanently waterlogged.\nIV. 85 to 90 percent of Bihar's rural households own less than 5 acres of land each.\n\nWhich of these statements are correct?",
