    "topic": "Governor/Governor General/Viceroy",
    "question": "Which of the following social reforms were started by\nWilliam Bentinck\n1. Abolition of Sati Pratha\n2. Abolition of slavery\n3. Removal of the provision of disqualification due to\nreligious conversion\n4. Suppression of organized gangs of thugs\nSelect the correct answer from the code given below-",
