    "question": "Indicate the true sequence of events concerning the\npostponement of Non-cooperation Movement :\n(1) Police firing in Chauri-Chaura\n(2) Police station set fired by violent crowd\n(3) Postponement of Movement by Gandhiji\n(4) Arresting of Gandhiji\nSelect your answer from the following codes –",
